Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.83,0:36:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,found out. They programmed the young\Nchildren in Germany from childhood in
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.20,0:36:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,which becoming a killer was like being a\Nboy scout with just good patriotism,
