Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.76,0:37:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You make it you wonder how anybody makes\Nit through.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.96,0:37:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, once devotion to truth then begins\Nto arm you. Because if that's your
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.07,0:37:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,priority, what it tends to do is expose\Nthat which is not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.24,0:37:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're committed to actually\Nknowing the truth and following the
