Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.83,0:37:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it tends to uh unearth and reveal\Nby your intentionality
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.64,0:37:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is detrimental to that\Nyour goal. That which is detrimental to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.24,0:37:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,your goal now becomes exposed.\NYou didn't realize that that person was
