Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.83,0:38:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right? So integrity then begins to\Nshake out that which is non- integrous
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.96,0:38:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and make it more visible. Make it more\Nvisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.24,0:38:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want peace, you have to be\Npeaceful. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.48,0:38:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It means you can't get into better than\Nothers. You can't mean that winning is
