Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.24,0:38:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,any significance. Why would I want the\Npeople in Ecuador to do it any different
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.80,0:38:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,way than they were doing it? I mean, to\Nme it was perfect. I should have moved
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.96,0:38:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to Ecuador like an idiot. I didn't. I\Ncame back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.88,0:38:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That to me is a perfect place to live.\NThey forgot about time years ago. And u
