Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.92,0:39:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,as a way of being in the world.\NSo like love which is not dualistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.72,0:39:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a this loves that. It's\Nlovingness is a state of being in the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.52,0:39:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,world. Consequently, peacefulness is an\Ninner choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.32,0:39:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And when one becomes\Nthat which out of which peace arises,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.83,0:39:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,peace does not arise out of\Nwinning the argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.35,0:39:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth doesn't just stand by itself and\Nas a hypothetical possibility. It
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.59,0:39:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes energized by devotion.\NSo devotional non-duality means
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.83,0:39:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that one is aligned with the fastest and\Nstraightest pathway to the realization
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.92,0:40:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of the presence of God within.\NOne is willing to sacrifice everything
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.56,0:40:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to it. And one is devoted to the task.\NOne is devoted to discovering what is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.59,0:40:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth or falsehood no matter what.\NTherefore, the reason we redid the
