Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.92,0:40:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,no way of discerning that it's totally\Ncorrupt and totally false.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.00,0:40:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I read scientific treatises all day long\Nthat the minute you pick up the article
